snippet.textDisplay: Hot take: It all sounds the same at this point. Sure this might be a banger but there’s no variety at this point. The songs are heavily aesthetic focused or probably just Hashim Ali effortlessly doing his job however in terms of music it pretty much sounds the same background template. And this season looks like they are desperately trying to recreate another Pasoori.
